dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for calling Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jordan Miller. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Jessica Bell.
Nice to meet you, Jessica! Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Yes, my policy number is five six eight two three one.
Thank you, Jessica. Could you also confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my date of birth is the twenty-fourth of July, nineteen eighty-eight.
Great, thank you for confirming that information, Jessica. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about today?
I wanted to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Let's proceed with the necessary details. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance, Jessica.
Thank you for your time, Jessica. Have a wonderful day!
